      "audio_text": "Bald eagles. Bald eagles are majestic, powerful hunting birds.",
      "sequence_num": 1
    },
    {
      "start_time": 15.060833333333335,
      "end_time": 18.480833333333333,
      "duration": 3.52,
      "audio_text": "They're a type of eagle, with distinct colors.",
