      "end_time": 23.640833333333333,
      "duration": 3.59,
      "audio_text": "And despite their name, they actually aren't bald.",
      "sequence_num": 3
    },
    {
      "start_time": 24.660833333333336,
      "end_time": 27.310833333333335,
      "duration": 2.75,
      "audio_text": "They have lovely white feathers on their heads and tails,",
